1
00:00:14,820 --> 00:00:16,320
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Hey, Yuu.</font></font>
（チト）ねえ ユー

2
00:00:16,610 --> 00:00:17,740
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">What?</font></font>
（ユーリ）何？

3
00:00:18,530 --> 00:00:20,080
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Where are we, exactly?</font></font>
（チト）ここはどこなんだろう

4
00:00:20,660 --> 00:00:24,290
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Dunno. It's white as far as the eye can see.</font></font>
（ユーリ）
さあ 見渡す限り真っ白だね

5
00:00:25,120 --> 00:00:28,460
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">It's almost like we're the only people in the world.</font></font>
（ユーリ）まるで世界に２人しか
いないみたいだね

6
00:00:29,040 --> 00:00:31,170
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">You sure have it easy, spouting off poetry.</font></font>
（チト）詩人は気楽だな

7
00:00:32,010 --> 00:00:36,300
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Meanwhile, I'm desperately trying to find us
a place for us to ride out the cold...</font></font>
こっちは寒さをしのげる場所を
探すのに必死だってのに…

8
00:00:38,340 --> 00:00:39,800
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">That, or...</font></font>
それとも…

9
00:00:39,789 --> 00:00:41,374
（チト）うううっ…

10
00:00:41,220 --> 00:00:49,270
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">We're actually already dead, and we're in
the pure-white world of the afterlife.</font></font>
（ユーリ）
実は２人とも もう死んでいて―

11
00:00:44,127 --> 00:00:47,130
真っ白な死後の世界にいる

12
00:00:48,798 --> 00:00:50,049
とか…

13
00:00:50,400 --> 00:00:52,230
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Don't say that; it's bad luck.</font></font>
縁起でもない

14
00:00:55,700 --> 00:00:58,280
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">And stop making snowballs.</font></font>
あと雪玉作るのやめろ

15
00:00:58,280 --> 00:01:01,160
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Aww, I was just starting to have fun!</font></font>
え～ 楽しくなってきたのにい

16
00:01:01,700 --> 00:01:05,660
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">My head feels heavy, and I'm really cold.</font></font>
頭が重い

17
00:01:04,272 --> 00:01:05,607
それにすごく寒い

18
00:01:06,080 --> 00:01:10,500
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Hey, did you know that the afterlife
is supposed to be really warm?</font></font>
（ユーリ）ねえ 知ってる？

19
00:01:07,692 --> 00:01:10,862
死後の世界ってあったかいんだって

20
00:01:10,840 --> 00:01:14,630
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">If that's true, then it doesn't look like we're dead yet.</font></font>
（チト）だったら私たちは
まだ死んでないみたいだな

21
00:01:15,075 --> 00:01:16,951
う… うううっ…

22
00:01:17,035 --> 00:01:21,623
（風の音）

23
00:01:21,510 --> 00:01:23,060
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Sure is cold...</font></font>
（ユーリ）寒いね…

24
00:01:27,504 --> 00:01:33,510
♪～

25
00:01:34,820 --> 00:01:40,780
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="Lato Semibold" size="44">Maybe today we should turn back</font></font>

26
00:01:42,280 --> 00:01:48,540
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="Lato Semibold" size="44">Maybe tomorrow we can go even further</font></font>

27
00:01:45,700 --> 00:01:48,870
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="44">{\an8}Girls' Last Tour</font></font>

28
00:01:48,870 --> 00:01:49,790
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="Lato Semibold" size="44">Creaking</font></font>

29
00:01:49,790 --> 00:01:53,800
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="Lato Semibold" size="44">I want to find the many happy things far away</font></font>

30
00:01:53,800 --> 00:01:57,550
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="Lato Semibold" size="44">Hope sparkling with light, moving, moving</font></font>

31
00:01:57,550 --> 00:02:01,260
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="Lato Semibold" size="44">Unending talk continues on forever</font></font>

32
00:02:01,260 --> 00:02:04,810
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="Lato Semibold" size="44">Goodbye loneliness, moving, moving</font></font>

33
00:02:04,810 --> 00:02:11,310
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="Lato Semibold" size="44">Just like solving a difficult puzzle</font></font>

34
00:02:11,310 --> 00:02:18,990
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="Lato Semibold" size="44">I'm sure we'll keep learning the things we want to learn</font></font>

35
00:02:18,990 --> 00:02:22,910
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="Lato Semibold" size="44">So with a 1, 2, 3 start walking</font></font>

36
00:02:22,910 --> 00:02:26,410
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="Lato Semibold" size="44">Today and tomorrow and yesterday are all the same</font></font>

37
00:02:26,410 --> 00:02:30,250
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="Lato Semibold" size="44">So with a 1, 2, 3 start walking</font></font>

38
00:02:30,250 --> 00:02:34,000
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="Lato Semibold" size="44">In the opposite direction the world is turning</font></font>

39
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:37,840
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="Lato Semibold" size="44">That's right, with a 1, 2, 3 start dancing</font></font>

40
00:02:37,840 --> 00:02:41,550
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="Lato Semibold" size="44">I want to forget today and tomorrow and yesterday</font></font>

41
00:02:41,550 --> 00:02:45,220
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="Lato Semibold" size="44">So with a 1, 2, 3 start moving</font></font>

42
00:02:45,220 --> 00:02:50,230
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="Lato Semibold" size="44">I'm sure that's the a-a-a-a-answer</font></font>

43
00:02:51,296 --> 00:02:56,301
～♪

44
00:03:05,910 --> 00:03:10,000
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">W-we've gotta find a place to rest soon...</font></font>
（チト）そ そろそろホントに
休める場所を見つけないと

45
00:03:10,000 --> 00:03:11,000
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Yeah...</font></font>
うん…

46
00:03:16,571 --> 00:03:18,406
はっ んん！

47
00:03:18,740 --> 00:03:21,075
（エンジンを吹かす音）

48
00:03:27,180 --> 00:03:28,680
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Yuu, wake up!</font></font>
あっ ユー 起きろ

49
00:03:29,970 --> 00:03:31,850
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">I'm not sleeping.</font></font>
寝てないよ…

50
00:03:32,253 --> 00:03:34,839
う… くう～ うう…

51
00:03:34,923 --> 00:03:37,383
はあっ… うう…

52
00:03:37,150 --> 00:03:40,240
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">A b-b-building...</font></font>
た た 建物…

53
00:03:43,530 --> 00:03:44,950
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">It's big.</font></font>
（ユーリ）ううっ…
（チト）大きい…

54
00:03:49,062 --> 00:03:51,314
ふう… ううう…

55
00:03:55,830 --> 00:03:58,840
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Wh-wh-what kind of building is it?</font></font>
（ユーリ）
なな… 何の施設だろう…

56
00:03:58,840 --> 00:04:01,010
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">N-no clue.</font></font>
（チト）さ さあな

57
00:04:01,010 --> 00:04:04,340
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Let's find a way in.</font></font>
入り口を… 探そ… おっ

58
00:04:11,890 --> 00:04:13,100
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Whew.</font></font>
（ユーリ）っと…

59
00:04:13,127 --> 00:04:17,090
（チト）
ハァ… ハァ… う～ ううっ…

60
00:04:20,860 --> 00:04:24,820
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="44">{\an8}72nd Surface
Power Plant</font></font>

61
00:04:22,440 --> 00:04:24,820
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">C-can't read it...</font></font>
よ 読めないな

62
00:04:26,320 --> 00:04:28,830
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">This facility's pretty old.</font></font>
相当古い施設だ

63
00:04:28,830 --> 00:04:30,740
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Don't know how to get in.</font></font>
入り口も分からない

64
00:04:31,290 --> 00:04:33,200
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Hey, look, look!</font></font>
（ユーリ）ねえ 見て見て

65
00:04:33,960 --> 00:04:35,330
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">What's up?</font></font>
（チト）ん？ どうした？

66
00:04:35,750 --> 00:04:39,710
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Th-that pipe doesn't have any snow on it at all.</font></font>
（ユーリ）あ あのパイプ
全然雪が積もってない

67
00:04:43,670 --> 00:04:45,300
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">It's melting?</font></font>
溶けてる…

68
00:04:48,340 --> 00:04:50,140
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">I-is it hot?!</font></font>
あっ 熱いのか！？

69
00:04:50,760 --> 00:04:52,430
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Lemme shoot it.</font></font>
（ユーリ）撃ってみよう

70
00:04:55,503 --> 00:04:57,922
ううう…

71
00:04:58,006 --> 00:05:00,133
（チト）んん… ん…

72
00:05:11,644 --> 00:05:12,645
ハァ…

73
00:05:12,937 --> 00:05:15,523
（チト）ううっ…

74
00:05:20,987 --> 00:05:22,488
（ユーリ）ハァ…

75
00:05:25,616 --> 00:05:27,243
（チト）う…

76
00:05:28,077 --> 00:05:29,203
（ユーリ）ん…

77
00:05:31,372 --> 00:05:32,832
んんっ…

78
00:05:47,030 --> 00:05:49,160
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">H-hot water!</font></font>
（チト）お お湯だ…

79
00:05:50,070 --> 00:05:51,740
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Hot water!</font></font>
お湯～

80
00:05:59,400 --> 00:06:01,277
（ユーリ）ああ～
（チト）ハァ～

81
00:06:04,500 --> 00:06:06,800
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Wh-what should we do?</font></font>
（ユーリ）ど どうする？

82
00:06:06,800 --> 00:06:08,880
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">What do you mean? C'mon.</font></font>
（チト）どうするって そりゃ…

83
00:06:20,730 --> 00:06:24,020
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">I'm glad we found a pipe in such good condition.</font></font>
具合のいい管があってよかったね～

84
00:06:24,020 --> 00:06:25,110
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Yeah.</font></font>
うん

85
00:06:26,530 --> 00:06:28,610
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">There we go: a bath.</font></font>
（ユーリ）できた… 風呂

86
00:06:28,610 --> 00:06:29,860
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Let's get in.</font></font>
（チト）入ろう

87
00:06:29,650 --> 00:06:33,570
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="44">{\an8}Bath</font></font>

88
00:06:39,107 --> 00:06:42,276
（チト）うううっ ハァ…

89
00:06:44,590 --> 00:06:45,710
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Hot!</font></font>
あちっ ぐ…

90
00:06:46,531 --> 00:06:48,199
（ユーリ）ハァ～
（チト）あ…

91
00:06:48,460 --> 00:06:50,930
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">The water feels really good, Chi!</font></font>
いい湯だよ ちーちゃん

92
00:06:51,300 --> 00:06:52,840
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Y-yeah.</font></font>
う うん…

93
00:06:57,208 --> 00:07:00,086
（チト）ああ… つ～ つつつ…
（ユーリ）ハァ～

94
00:07:00,419 --> 00:07:03,756
（チト）ん… ああっ ああ…

95
00:07:04,173 --> 00:07:06,634
（ユーリ･チト）ハァ～

96
00:07:10,110 --> 00:07:11,900
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Feels good...</font></font>
（チト）気持ちいい…

97
00:07:11,900 --> 00:07:14,530
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">how long has it been since we had a bath?</font></font>
お風呂なんて いつぶりだろ

98
00:07:14,530 --> 00:07:18,620
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">I think we've taken two since leaving Grandpa's.</font></font>
おじいさんの所を出てから
２回は入ったっけ？

99
00:07:18,620 --> 00:07:20,000
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Three.</font></font>
３回だよ

100
00:07:20,460 --> 00:07:23,500
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Huh. So this is our fourth.</font></font>
そっか～ じゃあ４回目だ
（チト）ハァ～

101
00:07:25,960 --> 00:07:27,670
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">I feel like I've been brought back to life.</font></font>
ハァ～ 生き返る

102
00:07:28,130 --> 00:07:30,670
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">This is paradise, pure paradise...</font></font>
（ユーリ）極楽～ 極楽～

103
00:07:32,034 --> 00:07:35,913
（湯船の中で息を吐く音）

104
00:07:36,140 --> 00:07:39,520
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Hey, what does "paradise" mean anyway?</font></font>
ねえ “極楽”って
どういう意味？

105
00:07:40,600 --> 00:07:42,770
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">It means the afterlife.</font></font>
ああ… 死後の世界って意味だな

106
00:07:43,560 --> 00:07:46,980
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">That's an unlucky thing to say
after we've been brought back to life.</font></font>
（ユーリ）せっかく生き返ったのに
縁起でもないね

107
00:07:47,570 --> 00:07:48,820
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Yeah.</font></font>
（チト）そうだな

108
00:07:49,594 --> 00:07:50,470
（ユーリ）ハハハハハ…

109
00:07:50,595 --> 00:07:51,429
（チト）フフフ…

110
00:07:51,512 --> 00:07:56,017
（ユーリとチトの笑い声）

111
00:08:00,120 --> 00:08:02,580
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Ugh, I'm getting dizzy.</font></font>
あ～ のぼせてきた

112
00:08:03,065 --> 00:08:05,943
（湯船の中で息を吐く音）

113
00:08:09,000 --> 00:08:12,970
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="44">{\an8}Journal</font></font>

114
00:08:16,537 --> 00:08:20,791
（きしむ音）

115
00:08:21,520 --> 00:08:23,640
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">The wind sure is blowing hard.</font></font>
すごい吹雪だね

116
00:08:23,640 --> 00:08:25,350
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Yeah, huh.</font></font>
うん そうだね

117
00:08:25,810 --> 00:08:28,650
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Glad we found a place we could stay.</font></font>
宿りできる場所があってよかったね

118
00:08:28,650 --> 00:08:30,730
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Yeah, huh.</font></font>
うん そうだね

119
00:08:31,690 --> 00:08:36,280
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">We went into a building and
blocked the entrance with snow.</font></font>
“私たちは建物に入り
入り口を雪で固めた”

120
00:08:36,280 --> 00:08:40,990
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">We were lucky to have scrap material
we could use to help retain heat.</font></font>
“保温のために役に立つ有機物の
廃材があったのは幸いだった”

121
00:08:42,040 --> 00:08:44,710
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Oh, add more fuel.</font></font>
あ 燃料追加して

122
00:08:45,120 --> 00:08:46,500
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Okay, okay.</font></font>
ヘイヘイ

123
00:08:46,500 --> 00:08:48,130
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">One okay is enough.</font></font>
ヘイは１回だ

124
00:08:48,500 --> 00:08:49,670
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Okay.</font></font>
（ユーリ）ヘ～イ

125
00:08:52,000 --> 00:08:56,590
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Must be nice for you, Chi,
making me do all the annoying work.</font></font>
ちーちゃんはいいよね

126
00:08:54,075 --> 00:08:56,661
めんどくさいことは私任せで

127
00:08:56,590 --> 00:09:00,050
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">If you don't have the brains, use your brawn.</font></font>
頭が足りないやつは
体動かすんだよ

128
00:09:00,050 --> 00:09:02,890
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">You can't even read or write.</font></font>
お前 ロクに読み書きも
できないだろ

129
00:09:03,220 --> 00:09:04,600
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Huh.</font></font>
あ～ う…

130
00:09:05,730 --> 00:09:07,650
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">What're you writing again?</font></font>
それ 何 書いてんだっけ？

131
00:09:07,900 --> 00:09:12,150
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">It's a journal or log I've been keeping since we left.</font></font>
出発してからの日記というか
日誌というか…

132
00:09:12,650 --> 00:09:14,690
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">I explained it to you before.</font></font>
前にも説明したろ

133
00:09:14,690 --> 00:09:15,610
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">You did?</font></font>
そだっけ

134
00:09:16,110 --> 00:09:21,200
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">People like you are exactly why
we need to have a journal like this.</font></font>
お前みたいなやつにこそ
こういう記録が必要なんだよ

135
00:09:22,030 --> 00:09:24,660
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Memories fade, so we write them down.</font></font>
記憶は薄れるから
記録しておくんだよ

136
00:09:26,148 --> 00:09:27,483
あ～

137
00:09:30,330 --> 00:09:33,340
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Memories just get in the way of living.</font></font>
記憶なんて生きる邪魔だぜ

138
00:09:34,510 --> 00:09:37,680
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Can you remember the last time you ate?</font></font>
ごはん食べたかどうかくらいは
覚えといてよ

139
00:09:38,300 --> 00:09:40,850
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Huh? Did we eat today?</font></font>
あれ？ 今日ごはん食べたっけ？

140
00:09:41,510 --> 00:09:43,180
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Seriously?</font></font>
食べたって ハァ…

141
00:09:45,220 --> 00:09:47,520
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Books are really amazing.</font></font>
本ってのはすごいんだよ

142
00:09:48,270 --> 00:09:54,690
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Ever since they were invented thousands of years ago,
humanity has been recording things in books.</font></font>
何千年も前に
古代人が発明して以来―

143
00:09:52,049 --> 00:09:54,885
ずっと人類は本に記録してきたんだ

144
00:09:54,690 --> 00:09:55,940
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Huh.</font></font>
（ユーリ）ふ～ん

145
00:09:56,240 --> 00:10:00,490
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">It's thanks to books that we can learn about
things that happened long ago.</font></font>
（チト）昔のことを
知ることができるのも―

146
00:09:58,889 --> 00:10:00,433
本のおかげだしね

147
00:10:01,200 --> 00:10:04,700
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">You've always liked books, huh, Chi.</font></font>
（ユーリ）ちーちゃんは昔から
本 好きだったもんね

148
00:10:04,700 --> 00:10:07,750
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">You read a whole lot of Grandpa's books.</font></font>
おじいさんの本
たくさん読んでたし

149
00:10:07,750 --> 00:10:10,370
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Yeah, but we had to burn most of them.</font></font>
（チト）
ほとんど燃えちゃったけどね

150
00:10:10,370 --> 00:10:14,750
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Excluding the couple of journals, we have...</font></font>
今も持ってるのは
数冊の日記を除けば…

151
00:10:14,750 --> 00:10:18,880
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">One, two, three... four books.</font></font>
１… ２… ３… ４冊か…

152
00:10:21,550 --> 00:10:22,600
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Lemme see.</font></font>
見せて

153
00:10:25,970 --> 00:10:27,020
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Sure.</font></font>

154
00:10:26,600 --> 00:10:27,350
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="44">{\an8}KAPPA
Akutagawa</font></font>
はい

155
00:10:29,503 --> 00:10:31,339
ふ～ん

156
00:10:33,230 --> 00:10:36,860
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">I wonder how many books are left in the world.</font></font>
世界中探しても
もうどれだけ残ってるか…

157
00:10:36,860 --> 00:10:38,490
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">I see.</font></font>
なるほど～

158
00:10:40,110 --> 00:10:43,870
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">The fire's getting low. Add more fuel.</font></font>
あっ 火 弱くなってる

159
00:10:42,308 --> 00:10:44,185
燃料追加して

160
00:10:44,200 --> 00:10:45,240
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Okay.</font></font>
はい

161
00:10:45,660 --> 00:10:49,000
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">We don't have much fuel left to burn.</font></font>
燃やせる物も
なくなってきたなあ

162
00:10:49,023 --> 00:10:50,191
よっ！

163
00:10:50,858 --> 00:10:51,859
あ…

164
00:10:52,210 --> 00:10:55,040
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">What, are we out of fuel?</font></font>
何？ 廃材 もうないの？

165
00:10:55,237 --> 00:10:56,572
ん…？

166
00:10:58,908 --> 00:11:01,077
あっ… うわああっ！

167
00:11:01,180 --> 00:11:03,010
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">The book!</font></font>
本がっ！！

168
00:11:03,010 --> 00:11:04,390
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Put it out!</font></font>
消せ～っ！
（ユーリ）熱っ 熱い…

169
00:11:04,390 --> 00:11:05,720
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Hot, hot!</font></font>

170
00:11:06,040 --> 00:11:09,794
ハァ ハァ ハァ ハァ…
（ユーリ）ううっ… ん？

171
00:11:09,877 --> 00:11:14,965
（チト）ああああ… 「河童(かっぱ)」が…

172
00:11:11,690 --> 00:11:13,770
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Not Kappa...</font></font>

173
00:11:15,341 --> 00:11:18,469
ああ…
（ユーリ）「河童」？

174
00:11:17,530 --> 00:11:18,530
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Kappa?</font></font>

175
00:11:18,980 --> 00:11:22,410
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">I literally just told you books were important!</font></font>
（ユーリ）うううっ…
（チト）本が大事ってこと―

176
00:11:20,513 --> 00:11:22,515
話したよな さっき

177
00:11:22,410 --> 00:11:25,620
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Sorry, I wasn't really listening!</font></font>
ごめん それは
あんまり聞いてなかった

178
00:11:25,620 --> 00:11:26,780
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Listen!</font></font>
聞けよっ！！

179
00:11:28,479 --> 00:11:29,438
ぷは～っ

180
00:11:29,522 --> 00:11:32,733
くう… ん！

181
00:11:33,080 --> 00:11:35,080
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">I said I was sorry.</font></font>
悪かったって

182
00:11:35,080 --> 00:11:37,130
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Moron! Idiot! Garbage!</font></font>
バカ！ クズ！ ゴミ！

183
00:11:37,630 --> 00:11:38,550
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Okay.</font></font>
はい

184
00:11:38,550 --> 00:11:39,550
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Don't "okay" me!</font></font>
“はい”じゃない

185
00:11:41,340 --> 00:11:43,510
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Whatever, I'm going to bed!</font></font>
もういい 寝るっ！

186
00:11:55,650 --> 00:11:56,900
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Chi.</font></font>
（ユーリ）ちーちゃん

187
00:12:14,316 --> 00:12:15,609
（ユーリ）ん…

188
00:12:28,350 --> 00:12:31,310
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="44">{\an8}Journal
Chito</font></font>

189
00:12:51,950 --> 00:12:54,160
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">C'mon, Yuu, hurry it up.</font></font>
（チト）ほら ユー 早くしろ

190
00:12:58,000 --> 00:13:00,750
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Chi, are you still mad at me?</font></font>
ちーちゃん まだ怒ってる？

191
00:13:00,750 --> 00:13:01,800
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">No.</font></font>
（チト）別に

192
00:13:01,800 --> 00:13:03,460
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">You definitely are.</font></font>
怒ってるじゃん

193
00:13:07,119 --> 00:13:08,496
あ…

194
00:13:11,310 --> 00:13:12,810
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Ready, go!</font></font>
（チト･ユーリ）せーの！

195
00:13:16,378 --> 00:13:17,796
あ…

196
00:13:23,280 --> 00:13:24,690
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">The storm cleared up!</font></font>
お～っ 晴れた

197
00:13:24,690 --> 00:13:26,030
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">The snow sure piled up.</font></font>
積もったな

198
00:13:29,110 --> 00:13:31,740
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">What do you think, doable?</font></font>
（ユーリ）ん… どう 行けそう？

199
00:13:31,740 --> 00:13:33,120
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Think so.</font></font>
何とか…

200
00:13:37,316 --> 00:13:38,317
ん？

201
00:13:40,460 --> 00:13:43,250
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Hey, are you still mad?</font></font>
ねえ まだ怒ってる？

202
00:13:48,050 --> 00:13:49,340
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">No.</font></font>
（チト）別に

203
00:13:52,600 --> 00:13:54,520
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Hurry up and get on.</font></font>
早く乗りなよ

204
00:13:55,220 --> 00:13:58,520
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Even if we lost a book, we still have the journals.</font></font>
本は減っても まあ
この日記があるし

205
00:14:02,860 --> 00:14:04,230
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Hup.</font></font>
よいしょっと

206
00:14:04,230 --> 00:14:08,240
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">If we keep writing things in our journal,
it'll be like a book...</font></font>
日記も書き連ねていけば
本のようなもの

207
00:14:10,200 --> 00:14:11,870
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">What is this?</font></font>
ん？ 何だ これ？

208
00:14:13,660 --> 00:14:16,080
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Hey, Yuu, you drew something in here, didn't you?</font></font>
おい ユー 何か落書きしたろ

209
00:14:16,750 --> 00:14:17,750
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Did I?</font></font>
はて？

210
00:14:18,000 --> 00:14:20,040
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Don't go drawing in here.</font></font>
落書きすんなよ

211
00:14:20,370 --> 00:14:23,090
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">What is this, even?</font></font>
何書いてあるんだ これ…

212
00:14:23,340 --> 00:14:25,300
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">It's your face, Chi.</font></font>
ちーちゃんの顔だよ

213
00:14:25,590 --> 00:14:27,880
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">My face doesn't look like this.</font></font>
（チト）私はこんな顔じゃない

214
00:14:27,880 --> 00:14:29,680
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">It's what you look like when you're asleep.</font></font>
だって寝顔だもん

215
00:14:31,787 --> 00:14:33,247
（チト）フゥ…

216
00:14:46,802 --> 00:14:49,680
（エンジン音）

217
00:14:53,530 --> 00:14:56,040
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">I wanna draw some more now.</font></font>
もっと落書きしたいなあ～

218
00:14:56,040 --> 00:14:58,450
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">We're short on paper, so don't.</font></font>
（チト）紙もったいないからダメ

219
00:14:58,450 --> 00:14:59,660
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Aww.</font></font>
（ユーリ）え～

220
00:14:59,660 --> 00:15:02,080
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">And you wrote a letter wrong.</font></font>
（チト）あと 字 間違えてるぞ

221
00:15:02,630 --> 00:15:03,710
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Huh?</font></font>
（ユーリ）え？

222
00:15:04,000 --> 00:15:09,010
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="44">{\an8}I'M SOKKY</font></font>

223
00:15:04,790 --> 00:15:06,420
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">"I'M SOKKY"?</font></font>
（チト）“ごぬんね”？

224
00:15:11,720 --> 00:15:13,550
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Think it's around here.</font></font>
（チト）この辺かな

225
00:15:13,550 --> 00:15:16,970
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Sure is nice out, despite it all.</font></font>
（ユーリ）
よく晴れてるねえ それにしても

226
00:15:17,720 --> 00:15:20,180
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">It's been nice out for a bit now.</font></font>
（チト）ここのところ晴れ続きだし

227
00:15:21,310 --> 00:15:24,190
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">That's why I figure it's gonna be coming soon.</font></font>
だから
そろそろ来るんじゃないかな

228
00:15:24,690 --> 00:15:26,440
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">What's coming?</font></font>
来るって何が？

229
00:15:27,190 --> 00:15:29,360
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">C'mon, you can hear it.</font></font>
（チト）ほら 音がする

230
00:15:28,302 --> 00:15:29,845
（チト）ほら 音がする

231
00:15:28,302 --> 00:15:29,845
（地響き）

232
00:15:29,845 --> 00:15:30,179
（地響き）

233
00:15:30,179 --> 00:15:31,347
（地響き）

234
00:15:30,179 --> 00:15:31,347
（ユーリ）あ…

235
00:15:31,347 --> 00:15:32,431
（地響き）

236
00:15:39,290 --> 00:15:40,620
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">There it is.</font></font>
（チト）お～ 来た来た

237
00:15:42,210 --> 00:15:44,790
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">The water from the melted snow.</font></font>
ほら 雪解け水が…

238
00:15:44,790 --> 00:15:47,670
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">So that's what you meant, the snow water.</font></font>
来るって雪解け水のことか…

239
00:15:48,380 --> 00:15:50,260
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Sure is a lot.</font></font>
すごい量だね

240
00:15:50,260 --> 00:15:53,130
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Because it's been warm now for a few days.</font></font>
（チト）数日前から
かなりあったかかったからね

241
00:15:53,130 --> 00:15:54,720
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">It must have really filled up.</font></font>
たまってたはずだよ

242
00:15:55,430 --> 00:15:58,510
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Why does a whole lot come out all at once?</font></font>
（ユーリ）なんで一度に
たくさん出てくるんだろう？

243
00:15:58,510 --> 00:16:03,060
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Because the ancient city's drainage system
is still here, or something.</font></font>
（チト）大昔の都市の排水機能が
残ってるせいだとか何とか…

244
00:16:04,310 --> 00:16:08,020
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">In any case, what's important is
we get some drinking water.</font></font>
とにかく大切なのは 飲み水の確保

245
00:16:08,230 --> 00:16:09,900
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">We going down on foot?</font></font>
徒歩で行くの？

246
00:16:09,900 --> 00:16:12,030
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Yeah, it can't get down there.</font></font>
そいつが降りられないからね

247
00:16:12,030 --> 00:16:12,990
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Hup.</font></font>
（ユーリ）よっこら
（チト）それと…

248
00:16:12,990 --> 00:16:13,860
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">That, and...</font></font>

249
00:16:14,098 --> 00:16:20,104
♪～

250
00:16:36,010 --> 00:16:38,260
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Gotta take our shoes off.</font></font>
靴を脱がなきゃ

251
00:16:42,751 --> 00:16:43,585
（ユーリ）んしょ

252
00:16:45,879 --> 00:16:48,632
（チト）う… うううっ…

253
00:16:48,480 --> 00:16:49,690
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Cold!</font></font>
冷たっ うう…

254
00:16:50,820 --> 00:16:52,530
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">So cold!</font></font>
冷た～ うっ…

255
00:16:53,178 --> 00:16:54,263
（チト･ユーリ）ううう…

256
00:16:56,320 --> 00:16:58,740
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">It's so blue, Chi.</font></font>
（ユーリ）
全部真っ青だね ちーちゃん

257
00:16:58,740 --> 00:17:00,780
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">It's like we're in the sky.</font></font>
空にいるみたいだよ

258
00:17:00,780 --> 00:17:02,790
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Watch your step.</font></font>
（チト）足元 気をつけろよ

259
00:17:02,790 --> 00:17:05,500
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">The water might've washed down something sharp.</font></font>
とがった物が
流れてきてるかもしれない

260
00:17:05,870 --> 00:17:08,170
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Let's look up while we walk, Chi.</font></font>
（ユーリ）
上を向いて歩こうよ ちーちゃん

261
00:17:08,170 --> 00:17:09,590
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Look up!</font></font>
上をさ

262
00:17:09,590 --> 00:17:12,710
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">I just told you to watch where you step.</font></font>
足元に気をつけろって
言ってんだろうが

263
00:17:12,960 --> 00:17:17,260
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">What a waste when the sky's so blue!</font></font>
もったいないな～
こんなに空が青いのに～

264
00:17:17,161 --> 00:17:17,995
（チト）ん…

265
00:17:19,600 --> 00:17:22,100
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">When the sky's so blue,</font></font>
こんなに空が青いし…

266
00:17:22,100 --> 00:17:25,140
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">it's good weather for a laundry day.</font></font>
今日は洗濯日和だな

267
00:17:25,140 --> 00:17:29,060
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="44">{\an8}Laundry</font></font>

268
00:17:33,070 --> 00:17:34,030
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Cold!</font></font>
（チト）寒っ

269
00:17:34,440 --> 00:17:36,320
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">What's this rope for?</font></font>
このヒモは何？

270
00:17:36,320 --> 00:17:38,660
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">We could get hurt if we get washed away by a current.</font></font>
流されたら危ないだろ
深い所もあるし

271
00:17:38,660 --> 00:17:40,660
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">The water gets deep in places, too.</font></font>

272
00:17:40,660 --> 00:17:42,410
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Are you gonna take off your helmet?</font></font>
ヘルメット取ったら？

273
00:17:43,200 --> 00:17:46,000
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">I could get hurt if I fell.</font></font>
転んだら危ないだろうが

274
00:17:46,960 --> 00:17:49,040
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Half-naked with a helmet...</font></font>
半裸ヘルメット…

275
00:17:52,630 --> 00:17:55,590
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Our clothes sure are pretty dirty.</font></font>
やっぱり結構 汚れてるなあ…

276
00:17:55,840 --> 00:17:59,010
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Why is the sky blue?</font></font>
空って なんで青いんだろうねえ

277
00:17:59,380 --> 00:18:02,600
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Hey, Yuu, why're you acting so laid back?</font></font>
おい ユー
なんでまったりしてんだ？

278
00:18:03,010 --> 00:18:04,850
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">I got the water.</font></font>
水なら くんだが

279
00:18:04,850 --> 00:18:07,180
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">You gotta wash your clothes, too.</font></font>
お前も服を洗うんだよ

280
00:18:07,180 --> 00:18:08,350
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Seriously?</font></font>
マジか

281
00:18:14,820 --> 00:18:18,280
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Hey, Chi, why is the sky blue?</font></font>
（ユーリ）ねえ ちーちゃん
空ってなんで青いの？

282
00:18:18,280 --> 00:18:22,570
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">People long ago said it was
reflecting the blue of the ocean.</font></font>
（チト）昔の人は海の青が
映っているからなんて言ってたり

283
00:18:22,570 --> 00:18:23,530
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">The ocean?</font></font>
（ユーリ）海？

284
00:18:23,530 --> 00:18:28,080
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">It's a place with water that's way bigger
and way deeper than this puddle.</font></font>
（チト）この水たまりよりも
ず～っと広く深く水がある場所だよ

285
00:18:28,750 --> 00:18:33,250
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">The water under our feet would go on forever.</font></font>
私たちの足元のず～っと下に
まだ あるとか ないとか…

286
00:18:33,630 --> 00:18:37,210
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">I heard people long ago lived by the ocean.</font></font>
昔の人は海のそばで
暮らしてたらしいけど

287
00:18:37,800 --> 00:18:39,420
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Hey, look, look, Chi!</font></font>
（ユーリ）
あっ 見て見て ちーちゃん！

288
00:18:39,420 --> 00:18:40,720
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">I told you to listen to-</font></font>
だから聞けよっ

289
00:18:40,720 --> 00:18:43,550
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Hey! You idiot, don't start running all of a sudden!</font></font>
…って わっ バカ！ 急に走るなっ

290
00:18:43,789 --> 00:18:44,581
うっ うわああっ！

291
00:18:44,832 --> 00:18:47,042
（転ぶ音）

292
00:18:54,570 --> 00:18:56,780
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">I'm glad I was wearing my helmet.</font></font>
ヘルメットかぶっててよかった…

293
00:18:56,780 --> 00:18:58,190
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">C'mon, look, look!</font></font>
（ユーリ）ねえ 見て見て
（チト）ん！

294
00:19:00,490 --> 00:19:02,780
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Why are you all wet, too?</font></font>
なんでユーも濡れてんだ？

295
00:19:03,200 --> 00:19:04,280
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">I fell.</font></font>
コケた

296
00:19:04,950 --> 00:19:06,700
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Forget that, look at this!</font></font>
それより見てっ これを

297
00:19:09,870 --> 00:19:12,170
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">It's... a fish.</font></font>
（チト）これは… 魚だな

298
00:19:12,710 --> 00:19:14,290
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Fish...</font></font>
（ユーリ）魚？

299
00:19:14,540 --> 00:19:16,590
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Looks like it's dead though.</font></font>
死んでるみたいだが

300
00:19:16,590 --> 00:19:18,630
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">What's a fish?</font></font>
魚って何なの？

301
00:19:18,630 --> 00:19:21,260
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">It's a living thing that lives in water.</font></font>
水の中に住む生き物だよ

302
00:19:21,550 --> 00:19:24,890
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">I heard there were a lot of them in the ocean long ago.</font></font>
昔は海とかに たくさんいたらしい

303
00:19:24,890 --> 00:19:29,140
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">I thought humans were the only
living things still out there...</font></font>
人以外の生き物なんて
もう生き残ってないと思ってたけど

304
00:19:32,730 --> 00:19:34,810
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Okay, let's eat it!</font></font>
よし 食べよう

305
00:19:34,810 --> 00:19:37,940
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">What? Can we eat it?</font></font>
え～ 食べられるかな ん～

306
00:19:40,240 --> 00:19:44,530
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">I heard people ate fish long ago,
but is this one okay?</font></font>
昔の人は食べてたらしいけど…
大丈夫かな

307
00:19:44,530 --> 00:19:47,450
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">It doesn't look like it's started to decompose...</font></font>
分解は始まってないみたいだけど
う～ん

308
00:19:49,620 --> 00:19:52,580
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Well, maybe we can eat it if we roast it.</font></font>
まあ 焼けば食べられるかな

309
00:19:52,580 --> 00:19:53,790
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Let's roast it!</font></font>
焼こう

310
00:19:53,790 --> 00:19:55,880
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">After we hang up our clothes to dry.</font></font>
（チト）洗った物 干してからね

311
00:19:56,069 --> 00:19:57,154
う…

312
00:19:58,050 --> 00:20:02,340
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Hey, I wonder what it feels like to live in the water.</font></font>
（ユーリ）ねえ―
水の中に住むってさ
どんな感じだろうね

313
00:20:02,590 --> 00:20:05,840
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Dunno. Probably floating, and sinking...</font></font>
さあ 浮いたり沈んだり…

314
00:20:05,840 --> 00:20:09,430
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">I heard they flap these fins to move forward.</font></font>
ここのヒレをパタパタさせて
進むらしいけど

315
00:20:09,770 --> 00:20:10,810
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Fins...</font></font>
ヒレ？

316
00:20:14,100 --> 00:20:16,940
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Maybe it swam like that.</font></font>
あんな感じで泳いでたのかな

317
00:20:16,940 --> 00:20:18,480
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Maybe.</font></font>
そうかもね

318
00:20:19,730 --> 00:20:21,490
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Should be done by now.</font></font>
そろそろ焼けたかな

319
00:20:21,490 --> 00:20:22,610
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Let's eat it!</font></font>
（ユーリ）食べるっ！

320
00:20:23,360 --> 00:20:25,910
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Be careful, it's hot.</font></font>
熱いから気をつけろよ

321
00:20:26,820 --> 00:20:28,120
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">All right!</font></font>
おっ おっ やった！ あちっ！

322
00:20:28,120 --> 00:20:29,200
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Hot!</font></font>

323
00:20:29,895 --> 00:20:31,104
あ…

324
00:20:32,272 --> 00:20:34,566
は～むっ

325
00:20:35,025 --> 00:20:37,361
ん… ん… ん… ん～

326
00:20:37,290 --> 00:20:39,040
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">H-how is it?</font></font>
ど どう？

327
00:20:38,820 --> 00:20:41,865
ん… ん？ ん… ん～

328
00:20:42,449 --> 00:20:46,995
ん… んん んん～

329
00:20:48,510 --> 00:20:49,430
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">It's good!</font></font>
うまい！

330
00:20:49,720 --> 00:20:51,100
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Let me try.</font></font>
私も

331
00:20:51,430 --> 00:20:53,350
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Don't eat all of it!</font></font>
あんまり食べないでよ

332
00:20:54,670 --> 00:20:55,712
はむっ

333
00:20:58,440 --> 00:21:00,730
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">I've never tasted anything like it.</font></font>
初めて食べる味だ

334
00:21:01,020 --> 00:21:02,610
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">It's weird.</font></font>
変な味

335
00:21:02,761 --> 00:21:03,971
はむっ

336
00:21:03,780 --> 00:21:06,030
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Me! I'm next!</font></font>
（ユーリ）次！ 次 私

337
00:21:06,181 --> 00:21:08,475
はむっ ん… ん…

338
00:21:12,120 --> 00:21:14,580
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Our clothes are all clean now.</font></font>
キレイになったね 服

339
00:21:18,130 --> 00:21:22,210
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">And these bones must feel refreshed
with all the meat cleaned off them.</font></font>
こっちは肉が落ちて
すっきりしたね 骨

340
00:21:22,210 --> 00:21:23,670
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Refreshed, huh...</font></font>
すっきりって

341
00:21:24,010 --> 00:21:27,510
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">But where did it come in from?</font></font>
でも どこから
流れてきたんだろうね

342
00:21:27,510 --> 00:21:32,060
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">It must have come in from a higher level, huh...</font></font>
（チト）
やっぱり上層からじゃないかな？

343
00:21:30,664 --> 00:21:32,749
排水に混じって

344
00:21:37,730 --> 00:21:41,520
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Maybe if we go up higher,
we'll find a whole bunch of them.</font></font>
（ユーリ）上のほうへ行けば
いっぱいいるのかな

345
00:21:41,520 --> 00:21:43,480
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">And what if we do?</font></font>
（チト）いたらどうするの？

346
00:21:43,480 --> 00:21:44,650
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">We eat them.</font></font>
（ユーリ）食べる

347
00:21:44,650 --> 00:21:45,940
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Eat them, huh...</font></font>
（チト）食べるか

348
00:21:45,940 --> 00:21:47,070
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Yeah.</font></font>
（ユーリ）うん

349
00:21:47,070 --> 00:21:48,160
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Yeah.</font></font>
（チト）そうだな

350
00:21:49,641 --> 00:21:53,353
（チト･ユーリ）ハァ～ ん～

351
00:21:55,522 --> 00:21:58,066
（２人の寝息）

352
00:22:04,990 --> 00:22:10,537
♪～

353
00:22:08,760 --> 00:22:11,100
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="Clear Sans Medium" size="42" color="#191211">{\an8}It's not over till it's over</font></font>

354
00:22:25,990 --> 00:22:29,740
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="Clear Sans Medium" size="42" color="#191211">{\an8}Where is this place I just woke up?</font></font>

355
00:22:29,740 --> 00:22:33,700
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="Clear Sans Medium" size="42" color="#191211">{\an8}What's going to start now?</font></font>

356
00:22:33,700 --> 00:22:37,540
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="Clear Sans Medium" size="42" color="#191211">{\an8}Before I realized it I'm getting ready to travel with you</font></font>

357
00:22:37,540 --> 00:22:42,170
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="Clear Sans Medium" size="42" color="#191211">{\an8}Let's go to a paradise sparkling in black and white (let's go)</font></font>

358
00:22:42,170 --> 00:22:43,540
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="Clear Sans Medium" size="42" color="#191211">{\an8}Let's make, let's make</font></font>

359
00:22:43,540 --> 00:22:45,800
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="Clear Sans Medium" size="42" color="#191211">{\an8}C'mon, let's make a world for you and me</font></font>

360
00:22:45,800 --> 00:22:47,420
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="Clear Sans Medium" size="42" color="#191211">{\an8}Let's start, let's start</font></font>

361
00:22:47,420 --> 00:22:49,550
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="Clear Sans Medium" size="42" color="#191211">{\an8}What should we start with? (huh?!)</font></font>

362
00:22:49,550 --> 00:22:51,300
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="Clear Sans Medium" size="42" color="#191211">{\an8}Let's dance, let's dance</font></font>

363
00:22:51,300 --> 00:22:53,550
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="Clear Sans Medium" size="42" color="#191211">{\an8}Let's be happy and dance! (yay, yay!)</font></font>

364
00:22:53,550 --> 00:22:57,140
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="Clear Sans Medium" size="42" color="#191211">{\an8}Our last trip is beginning (beginning)</font></font>

365
00:22:57,140 --> 00:23:01,150
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="Clear Sans Medium" size="42" color="#191211">{\an8}The world made up of just the two of us</font></font>

366
00:23:01,150 --> 00:23:05,480
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="Clear Sans Medium" size="42" color="#191211">{\an8}Is still spinning today (around and around)</font></font>

367
00:23:05,480 --> 00:23:08,900
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="Clear Sans Medium" size="42" color="#191211">{\an8}Today and tomorrow and the day after that</font></font>

368
00:23:08,900 --> 00:23:14,370
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="Clear Sans Medium" size="42" color="#191211">{\an8}Can I stay by your side?</font></font>

369
00:23:14,370 --> 00:23:15,120
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="Clear Sans Medium" size="42" color="#191211">{\an8}Please</font></font>

370
00:23:15,120 --> 00:23:19,120
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="Clear Sans Medium" size="42" color="#191211">{\an8}Not over yet, not over yet... (Travel)</font></font>

371
00:23:19,120 --> 00:23:23,080
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="Clear Sans Medium" size="42" color="#191211">{\an8}Not over yet, not over yet... (Journey)</font></font>

372
00:23:23,080 --> 00:23:26,960
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="Clear Sans Medium" size="42" color="#191211">{\an8}Not over yet, not over yet... (One more time!)</font></font>

373
00:23:26,960 --> 00:23:29,800
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="Clear Sans Medium" size="42" color="#191211">{\an8}Not over yet, not over yet... (Yes!)</font></font>

374
00:23:29,800 --> 00:23:31,840
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="Clear Sans Medium" size="42" color="#191211">{\an8}Journey</font></font>

375
00:23:36,430 --> 00:23:37,640
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Farewell.</font></font>
さらば

376
00:23:37,640 --> 00:23:39,140
<font color="#ffff54"><font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="52">Bye bye!</font></font>
バイバ～イ
